<br>
A legit reason to pour points into AGI - get your AGI to 100.  When you are alsmot dead, AGI gets reduced by a max of 25 percent.  If your AGI is 100 or higher normally, you never go below the 75 and start getting those nasty penalties to your running and to your AC (which just makes a really bad moment even worse).<br>
<br>
AGI is the hardest stat for a warrior to find, and I think if I rerolled my Ogre Warrior I'd give it all the AGI I could, just so it's closer to 100 when naked. <p><select name=Toadstomp Squishgood>
